RHEL 6, Install:

1. yum install mongodb-server
2. from the splice-repo install  django, mongoengine, kitchen, django-tastypie, django-tastypie-mongoengine
3. git clone git://github.com/jschrewe/django-mongodbforms.git
  * python setup.py install
4. from rpm or dev setup
  * install splice-server
  * install rhic-serve



